    {"id":"G058","en":"Date of Separation","es":"Fecha de Separación","zh":"分居日期","vi":"Ngày Ly Thân","ko":"별거일","ar":"تاريخ الانفصال","ht":"Dat Separasyon","pt":"Data de Separação","ru":"Дата разделения","tl":"Petsa ng Paghihiwalay","so":"Taariikhda Kala-tagga","ti":"ዕለት ምፍልላይ","am":"የመለያየት ቀን","definition_en":"The date one spouse expressed intent to end the marriage, affecting property division."},
    {"id":"G059","en":"Automatic Temporary Restraining Orders","es":"Órdenes de Restricción Temporales Automáticas","zh":"自动临时限制令","vi":"Lệnh Cấm Tạm Thời Tự Động","ko":"자동 임시 접근금지 명령","ar":"أوامر تقييد مؤقتة تلقائية","ht":"Lòd Restriksyon Tanporè Otomatik","pt":"Ordens de Restrição Temporárias Automáticas","ru":"Автоматические временные запретительные приказы","tl":"Awtomatikong Pansamantalang Restraining Orders","so":"Amarro Xayiraad Ku-meel-gaar ah oo Toos ah","ti":"ኣውቶማቲክ ግዝያዊ ናይ ምእጋድ ትእዛዛት","am":"ራስ-ሰር ጊዜያዊ እገዳ ትዕዛዞች","definition_en":"Standard orders in family law summons preventing both parties from certain actions."},
    {"id":"G060","en":"Family Court Services","es":"Servicios del Tribunal de Familia","zh":"家庭法院服务","vi":"Dịch Vụ Tòa Gia Đình","ko":"가정법원 서비스","ar":"خدمات محكمة الأسرة","ht":"Sèvis Tribinal Fanmi","pt":"Serviços do Tribunal de Família","ru":"Службы семейного суда","tl":"Family Court Services","so":"Adeegyada Maxkamadda Qoyska","ti":"ኣገልግሎት ቤት ፍርዲ ስድራቤት","am":"የቤተሰብ ፍርድ ቤት አገልግሎቶች","definition_en":"Court-connected services providing custody mediation and recommendations."}
